<p>网络测试-PING</p>
<p><font color=red>!!!IPV6模式下，必须填写完整地址，禁止双冒号省略，否则不予处理!!!</font></p>
<form name="ping" action="./ping.cgi" method="get">
<table>
<tr>
<td>域名</td>
<td><input type="text" name="domain" ></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>次数</td>
<td><input type="number" name="t" min="1" max="10" value="5">(1-10)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>类型</td>
<td>
<input type="radio" name="type" value="IPV4" checked>IPV4
<input type="radio" name="type" value="IPV6">IPV6
</td>
</tr>
</tr>
</form> 
</table>
<input type="submit" value="提交">
<input type="reset" value="重置">
</form>

